      <title>加拿大央行将基准利率下调至 4.5%</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-07-24/bank-of-canada-cuts-key-rate-to-4-5</link>
      <description><![CDATA[加拿大央行周三将利率下调 25 个基点至 4.5%。行长 Tiff Macklem 表示，通胀率回升至 2%“指日可待”，预计进一步降息也是合理的。（来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-07-24/bank-of-canada-cuts-key-rate-to-4-5</guid>
