    <item>
      <title>爱沙尼亚计划将 GDP 的 4% 用于国防开支以遏制俄罗斯</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-24/estonia-targets-4-of-gdp-for-defense-spending-to-deter-russia</link>
      <description><![CDATA[爱沙尼亚计划在未来两年内将国防开支提高到国内生产总值的4%，这是北约中最高水平之一，用于购买弹药并在俄罗斯入侵乌克兰后加强国家安全。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-24/estonia-targets-4-of-gdp-for-defense-spending-to-deter-russia</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 24 Jul 2024 15:09:55 GMT</pubDate>
